Located in the newest Industrial Park in Paradise, this 22,800 industrial building is vacant and ready for sublease on Bremigen's Boulevard. Current tenant has over 1 year remaining on current term, but longer term tenants welcomed by current Landlord. The building was custom built for current tenant and includes 20,000 sf warehouse with crane. Ceiling height is 24 feet and 1 grade level warehouse door. Smaller garage area and garage door located separate from the main warehouse- great for smaller shipping and receiving requirements. Large turn around area outside that is fenced in along with ample laydown space. Front office is 2800 and consists of reception, 2 large offices, boardroom, storage room and large kitchen. The building shows as brand new and is a wonderful opportunity to offset rents with the sublease rate. Sub-Tenant pays own utilities and operating.
